title: Shannon and the Clams play "Bean Fields" at The Current #music #shorts

description:
Indie rock band Shannon and the Clams perform three songs at The Current
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube  

Bay Area four-piece indie-rock band Shannon and the Clams visited The Current for a studio session hosted by Jessica Paxton. Watch the band's three-song set above.

Songs Performed
00:00:00 Bean Fields
00:03:05 What You’re Missing
00:05:51 Real Or Magic
All songs from Shannon and the Clams’ 2024 album, "The Moon Is In The Wrong Place," available on @EasyEyeSound.

Musicians
Shannon Shaw – vocals, bass
Cody Blanchard – vocals, guitar
William Sprott – keyboards, vocals
Nathaniel Mahan – drums, vocals
